summary: cousins outing day!! we went out and watched final destination 6 — it was such a blast. after the movie, we grabbed kfc at the mall and did some shopping at miniso. later, i headed over to my aunt’s house and i'm still here right now. after dinner, all of us cousins sat on the couch and watched a horror movie called 'friend request' on amazon prime. it was terrifying and amazing at the same time — we screamed and laughed so much. i honestly love spending time with them. i’m sleeping over here tonight. good night! i really enjoyed today.
